  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>With a large array of restaurants available in Levi, the Design Hotel is offered on a bed &amp; breakfast basis.  Breakfast is included and served in the Kekäle Restaurant. The restaurant specialises in serving season and organic products but of course, classic continental options will also be available.</p>
<p>A Festive Feast, a Christmas celebration meal with games and music, is included on the final night of your holiday. Please note that the Festive Feast will replace your last half-board dinner.</p>
<p> </p>]]></cateringDescription>
